```

## Important Configurations

### Next.js Config
- Configure image domains in next.config.js
- Implement rewrites for API routes
- Configure security headers

### TypeScript Config
- Enable strict mode
- Configure path mapping
- Use baseUrl for absolute imports

### ESLint Config
- Use @typescript-eslint/recommended
- Configure React Hooks rules
- Implement unused imports detection

## Performance

### Bundle Size
- Use dynamic imports for code splitting
- Implement lazy loading for heavy components
- Monitor bundle size with @next/bundle-analyzer

### Runtime Performance
- Use React.memo for pure components
- Implement useMemo for heavy calculations
- Use useCallback for functions passed as props

## Security

### Sensitive Data
- Never expose API keys on client-side
- Use environment variables for configurations
- Implement input sanitization

### Authentication
- Use AuthContext on src/context/Authentication/AuthContext.tsx for user management
- Implement refresh tokens
- Configure CORS properly

### Analytics
- Configure Vercel Analytics for performance

### Logging
- Use console.error for errors
- Implement structured logging
- Configure appropriate log levels